<!-- Cards Placeholder end -->

<div class="container-fluid text-dark">

    <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->

    <div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-custom rounded-3">
      <div class="container-fluid py-5" style="text-align: justify;">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Welcome to AIIMS Jodhpur</h1>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4">AIIMS Jodhpur is one of the SIX NEW AIIMS established by the Ministry of Health & Family Welfare, Government of India under the Pradhan Mantri Swasthya Suraksha Yojna (PMSSY) with the aim of correcting regional imbalances in quality tertiary level healthcare in the country and attaining self sufficiency in graduate and postgraduate medical education. PMSSY planned to set up 6 new AIIMS like institutions in under served areas of the country.</p>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4">These institutions are being established by an Act of Parliament on the lines of the original All India Institute of Medical Sciences in New Delhi which imparts both undergraduate and postgraduate medical education in all its branches and related fields, along with nursing and paramedical training to bring together in one place educational facilities of the highest order for the training of personnel in all branches of health care activity.</p>
        <h3 class="fw-bold">Jan Aushadhi Kendra</h3>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4">Our Jan Aushadhi Kendra has been proudly awarded for achieving the <b>highest sales in the state of Rajasthan for the second consecutive time</b>. This remarkable achievement reflects the dedication of our team and the strong trust of the community in affordable generic medicines.</p>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4">This success has been achieved under the <b>guidance and direction of Executive Director Shri Goverdhan Dutt Puri</b>, whose leadership and vision have played a key role in expanding access to quality medicines at affordable prices.</p>
        <p class="col-md-12 fs-4">This recognition motivates us to continue serving the public with commitment and to support the mission of providing quality medicines at affordable prices for all.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row align-items-md-stretch">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-custom rounded-3">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Executive Director's Vision</h1>
        <p class="fs-4" style="text-align: justify;">AIIMS Jodhpur is a center of clinical excellence serving the people of Western India. My vision as its Executive Director is to expand its footprint of achievement to span the latest advances in compassionate clinical care for patients and their families, cutting-edge research to improve outcomes, engaging educational environment for medical and nursing students, physicians, ancillary staff, and scientists, as well as a culture of collaboration and support as we all move forward together. Through outreach centers, we will aim to improve access to top-quality healthcare to everyone regardless of their location or economic status. Through reinvigorated training programs we will promote continuous learning through all stages of the career for all medical providers. Through enhancing the work with biotechnology, we will leverage the benefits of automation to reduce burnout and improve efficiency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-custom rounded-3">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Calendar</h1>
        <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FullCalendar Event Info on Click</title>
    
    <link href="calendar/css/fullcalendar.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Set the container size to 350px */
        #calendar {
            /*width: 350px;
            height: 350px;
            margin: 0 auto;  Centers the calendar */
        }
        .box {
        float: left;
        height: 15px;
        width: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border: 1px solid black;
        clear: both;
        }

        .red {
        background-color: red;
        }

        .green {
        background-color: green;
        }

        .blue {
        background-color: blue;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div id="calendar"></div>
</div>

<!-- Modal for displaying event details -->
<div class="modal fade" id="eventModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="eventModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="eventModalLabel">Event Details</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p><strong>Title:</strong> <span id="eventTitle"></span></p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> <span id="eventStart"></span></p>
                <!--<p><strong>End:</strong> <span id="eventEnd"></span></p>-->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

